Additions for Production-Readiness
	•	Environment switching:
Use System.getProperty() or .env to switch base URI per environment (dev, stage, prod).
	•	Dynamic spec fetching:
Fetch spec from an API gateway or URL if maintained externally.
	•	Mock server setup:
Include WireMock for testing edge cases (e.g., 500 errors).
	•	Reporting:
Integrate with Allure or custom reporting to show request/response/validation results.
	•	Run via Maven/CI:

mvn test



